Pressure Cooker: Chef vs. Chef - Season 1, Episode 3




Duff Goldman vs. Hugh Acheson

Host Anne-Marie Withenshaw welcomes Ace of Cakes star and guest chef Duff Goldman who keeps things on track as the belts pile the pressure on home cooks Craig Lund and Melanie Robinot. Anne-Marie also introduces Top Chef's Hugh Acheson who brings it with all his unique kitchen knowledge in mentoring home cooks Cathy Christoff and Jackie Goldhar. It's one of the most intense final rounds of the season and another difficult decision for tasting expert Giles Coren.




Original Air Date: 07-Feb-2015
